    description: 'Modern human-centric lighting design for 3 floors of premium office workspace, focusing on occupant health and productivity.',
    challenge: 'Creating a modern office that complies with WELL Building Standards. The environment required high color rendering index (CRI > 90) and uniform lighting layout to avoid eye strain during long screen usage, with automated brightness adjustments based on natural daylight.',
